			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "- Load up GustavDev/BGO_Main_A\r\n- Use the debugbook to go to Carmen's cosmetics shop\r\n- Carmen will be doing this AD during her behaviour loop inside the shop.\r\n- When she is at the box of fabrics, she will do the left-side ADs.\r\n- After that, she will walk over to a mannequin and play this dialogue again, this time saying the right-side ADs.\r\n- The lines sequence goes from down to up - the left and right ADs are matched horizontally."
				},
